      "day": 49,
      "content": "Hitting hard rate limits mid-sprint with NovaMind Assistant\u2014workflow completely stalled while waiting for quota reset. Anyone else running into this? \n\nThe support response time is solid (got acknowledgment within 2h), but the fundamental issue remains: no graceful degradation, no overflow handling, just a hard stop. For automation-heavy workflows this is brutal.\n\nCurious if others have worked around this or if there's a tier I'm missing. The platform itself is doing what it's supposed to, but the usage model needs rethinking for power users doing batch operations.",
